		<title type="html"><![CDATA[HTML Media Capture is now a W3C Recommendation]]></title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.w3.org/blog/news/archives/6812" />
		<id>https://www.w3.org/blog/news/?p=6812</id>
